ckground-color:#F8F7F4;border:1px solid #F1F5F9;border-radius:16px;padding:22px;margin:0 0 20px 0"><p style="margin:0 0 8px 0;font-size:11px;font-weight:600;letter-spacing:0.08em;text-transform:uppercase;color:#2563EB">Secure sign-in</p><h1 style="margin:0 0 8px 0;font-size:24px;font-weight:600;color:#1E293B;font-family:-apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &#x27;Segoe UI&#x27;, Roboto, &#x27;Helvetica Neue&#x27;, Arial, sans-serif;letter-spacing:-0.5px;line-height:1.25">Your sign-in link is ready</h1><p style="margin:0;font-size:14px;color:#5F6F85;line-height:1.5">No password. No waiting room.</p></div><p style="margin:0 0 12px 0;font-size:16px;color:#475569;line-height:1.6">Hello,</p><p style="margin:0 0 12px 0;font-size:16px;color:#475569;line-height:1.6">Tap the button below to open InstantMed, then confirm to sign in. The one-time link expires in 60 minutes.</p><table role="presentation" cellPadding="0" cellSpacing="0" style="margin:16px auto;width:100%"><tbody><tr><td style="text-align:center"><a href="https://example.com/auth/confirm#token_hash=abc&amp;type=magiclink" class="email-button email-button-primary" style="display:inline-block;padding:14px 32px;box-sizing:border-box;min-height:48px;font-size:16px;font-weight:600;line-height:20px;text-decoration:none;border-radius:12px;letter-spacing:0.01em;box-shadow:0 2px 8px rgba(37,99,235,0.25);background-color:#2563EB;color:#ffffff">Open InstantMed</a></td></tr></tbody></table><div class="email-box" style="background-color:#EFF6FF;border:1px solid #BFDBFE;border-radius:10px;padding:16px 20px;margin:14px 0"><p style="margin:0;font-size:13px;color:#1D4ED8;line-height:1.6">If this link has expired, request a fresh one from the sign-in page.</p></div><div class="email-box" style="background-color:#F5F7F9;border:1px solid #E2E8F0;border-radius:10px;padding:16px 20px;margin:14px 0"><p style="margin:0 0 8px 0;font-size:13px;font-weight:600;color:#1E293B;line-height:1.5">Copy this secure link</p><a href="https://example.com/auth/confirm#token_hash=abc&amp;type=magiclink" style="display:block;color:#2563EB;font-size:12px;line-height:1.5;text-decoration:none;word-break:break-all;overflow-wrap:anywhere">https://example.com/auth/confirm#token_hash=abc&amp;type=magiclink</a></div><p style="margin:0 0 12px 0;font-size:13px;color:#5F6F85;line-height:1.6;text-align:center">Didn&#x27;t ask for this? No stress. Ignore this email and nothing changes on your account.</p><p style="margin:0 0 12px 0;font-size:13px;color:#5F6F85;line-height:1.6;text-align:center;margin-top:4px">Button playing up? <a href="https://instantmed.com.au/sign-in" style="color:#2563EB;text-decoration:none">Open the sign-in page</a></p></td></tr><tr><td class="email-footer" style="padding:0;border-top:1px solid #F1F5F9;background-color:#F8F7F4"><table role="presentation" cellPadding="0" cellSpacing="0" style="width:100%"><tbody><tr><td style="padding:20px 40px;text-align:center"><p style="margin:0 0 6px 0;font-size:12px;color:#5F6F85;line-height:1.8;font-family:-apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &#x27;Segoe UI&#x27;, Roboto, &#x27;Helvetica Neue&#x27;, Arial, sans-serif"><a href="https://instantmed.com.au/privacy" style="color:#5F6F85;text-decoration:none">Privacy</a><span style="margin:0 8px;color:#E2E8F0">·</span><a href="https://instantmed.com.au/terms" style="color:#5F6F85;text-decoration:none">Terms</a><span style="margin:0 8px;color:#E2E8F0">·</span><a href="__UNSUBSCRIBE_URL__" style="color:#5F6F85;text-decoration:none">Manage preferences</a></p><p style="margin:0 0 6px 0;font-size:11px;color:#5F6F85;font-family:-apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &#x27;Segoe UI&#x27;, Roboto, &#x27;Helvetica Neue&#x27;, Arial, sans-serif">Made with care in Australia 🌤️ · Reviewed by AHPRA-registered doctors</p><p style="margin:0;font-size:11px;color:#5F6F85;font-family:-apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &#x27;Segoe UI&#x27;, Roboto, &#x27;Helvetica Neue&#x27;, Arial, sans-serif">InstantMed Pty Ltd · ABN 64 694 559 334 · Level 1/457-4