x solid #BBF7D0;border-radius:8px;padding:20px 24px;margin-bottom:24px"><p style="margin:0;font-size:14px;color:#15803D;font-weight:600">Medical Certificate</p><p style="margin:4px 0 0 0;font-size:18px;color:#1E293B;font-weight:600">Test Patient</p></div><p style="margin:0 0 12px 0;font-size:16px;color:#475569;line-height:1.6">Dear Sir/Madam,</p><p style="margin:0 0 12px 0;font-size:16px;color:#475569;line-height:1.6"><strong>Test Patient</strong> has requested that we forward their medical certificate to you. This certificate was issued by a registered Australian doctor through InstantMed&#x27;s telehealth service.</p><table role="presentation" cellPadding="0" cellSpacing="0" style="margin:16px auto;width:100%"><tbody><tr><td style="text-align:center"><a href="https://instantmed.com.au/dl/test" class="email-button email-button-primary" style="display:inline-block;padding:14px 32px;box-sizing:border-box;min-height:48px;font-size:16px;font-weight:600;line-height:20px;text-decoration:none;border-radius:12px;letter-spacing:0.01em;box-shadow:0 2px 8px rgba(37,99,235,0.25);background-color:#2563EB;color:#ffffff">Download Certificate (PDF)</a></td></tr></tbody></table><p style="margin:0 0 12px 0;font-size:13px;color:#5F6F85;line-height:1.6;text-align:center">This link expires in 7 days for security.</p><p style="margin:0 0 12px 0;font-size:13px;color:#5F6F85;line-height:1.6">InstantMed is an Australian telehealth service. All certificates are issued by AHPRA-registered doctors. Questions about this certificate? Please visit our <a href="https://instantmed.com.au/contact" style="color:#2563EB;font-weight:500">help centre</a>.</p></td></tr><tr><td class="email-footer" style="padding:0;border-top:1px solid #F1F5F9;background-color:#F8F7F4"><table role="presentation" cellPadding="0" cellSpacing="0" style="width:100%"><tbody><tr><td style="padding:20px 40px;text-align:center"><p style="margin:0 0 6px 0;font-size:12px;color:#5F6F85;line-height:1.8;font-family:-apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &#x27;Segoe UI&#x27;, Roboto, &#x27;Helvetica Neue&#x27;, Arial, sans-serif"><a href="https://instantmed.com.au/privacy" style="color:#5F6F85;text-decoration:none">Privacy</a><span style="margin:0 8px;color:#E2E8F0">·</span><a href="https://instantmed.com.au/terms" style="color:#5F6F85;text-decoration:none">Terms</a><span style="margin:0 8px;color:#E2E8F0">·</span><a href="__UNSUBSCRIBE_URL__" style="color:#5F6F85;text-decoration:none">Manage preferences</a></p><p style="margin:0 0 6px 0;font-size:11px;color:#5F6F85;font-family:-apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &#x27;Segoe UI&#x27;, Roboto, &#x27;Helvetica Neue&#x27;, Arial, sans-serif">Made with care in Australia 🌤️ · Reviewed by AHPRA-registered doctors</p><p style="margin:0;font-size:11px;color:#5F6F85;font-family:-apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &#x27;Segoe UI&#x27;, Roboto, &#x27;Helvetica Neue&#x27;, Arial, sans-serif">InstantMed Pty Ltd · ABN 64 694 559 334 · Level 1/457-459 Elizabeth St, Surry Hills NSW 2010</p></td></tr></tbody></table></td></tr></tbody></table></td></tr></tbody></table></body></html>"
`;

