 20px"><div style="display:inline-block;width:48px;height:48px;border-radius:50%;background-color:#F0FDF4;border:1px solid #BBF7D0;line-height:48px;text-align:center;font-size:22px;color:#15803D;margin-bottom:12px">💊</div><h1 style="margin:0 0 4px 0;font-size:22px;font-weight:700;color:#1E293B;letter-spacing:-0.4px;line-height:1.4;font-family:-apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &#x27;Segoe UI&#x27;, Roboto, &#x27;Helvetica Neue&#x27;, Arial, sans-serif">Your eScript is on its way</h1><p style="margin:0;font-size:13px;color:#5F6F85">Check your phone for the SMS</p></div><p style="margin:0 0 12px 0;font-size:16px;color:#475569;line-height:1.6">Test,</p><p style="margin:0 0 12px 0;font-size:16px;color:#475569;line-height:1.6">Your prescription has been approved and the eScript is heading to your phone via SMS. Take your phone to any pharmacy. The pharmacist will scan the QR code to dispense your medication. Bring your Medicare card for any PBS subsidy.</p><table role="presentation" cellPadding="0" cellSpacing="0" style="margin:16px auto;width:100%"><tbody><tr><td style="text-align:center"><a href="https://instantmed.com.au/track/REQ-TEST" class="email-button email-button-secondary" style="display:inline-block;padding:12px 28px;box-sizing:border-box;min-height:48px;font-size:16px;font-weight:600;line-height:22px;text-decoration:none;border-radius:12px;letter-spacing:0.01em;box-shadow:none;background-color:transparent;color:#1E293B;border:1px solid #E2E8F0">View request</a></td></tr></tbody></table></td></tr><tr><td class="email-footer" style="padding:0;border-top:1px solid #F1F5F9;background-color:#F8F7F4"><table role="presentation" cellPadding="0" cellSpacing="0" style="width:100%"><tbody><tr><td style="padding:20px 40px;text-align:center"><p style="margin:0 0 6px 0;font-size:12px;color:#5F6F85;line-height:1.8;font-family:-apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &#x27;Segoe UI&#x27;, Roboto, &#x27;Helvetica Neue&#x27;, Arial, sans-serif"><a href="https://instantmed.com.au/privacy" style="color:#5F6F85;text-decoration:none">Privacy</a><span style="margin:0 8px;color:#E2E8F0">·</span><a href="https://instantmed.com.au/terms" style="color:#5F6F85;text-decoration:none">Terms</a><span style="margin:0 8px;color:#E2E8F0">·</span><a href="__UNSUBSCRIBE_URL__" style="color:#5F6F85;text-decoration:none">Manage preferences</a></p><p style="margin:0 0 6px 0;font-size:11px;color:#5F6F85;font-family:-apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &#x27;Segoe UI&#x27;, Roboto, &#x27;Helvetica Neue&#x27;, Arial, sans-serif">Made with care in Australia 🌤️ · Reviewed by AHPRA-registered doctors</p><p style="margin:0;font-size:11px;color:#5F6F85;font-family:-apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &#x27;Segoe UI&#x27;, Roboto, &#x27;Helvetica Neue&#x27;, Arial, sans-serif">InstantMed Pty Ltd · ABN 64 694 559 334 · Level 1/457-459 Elizabeth St, Surry Hills NSW 2010</p></td></tr></tbody></table></td></tr></tbody></table></td></tr></tbody></table></body></html>"
